nodes.text: Dilu Miah is a creature and droid performer who portrayed a Takodana alien known as "Puffer" on set in Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens, Leevan Tenza and Mennis Duren in Rogue One: A Star Wars Story, one of the Caretakers in Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi, and Gelan Yees in Solo: A Star Wars Story.
